flowchart TD
    Dev[Developer / Platform Engineer] --> GitHub[GitHub]

    GitHub --> InfraRepo[homelab-infrastructure<br/>Ansible + Terraform]
    GitHub --> GitOpsRepo[homelab-gitops<br/>ArgoCD Applications]
    GitHub --> BackendRepo[secure-banking-platform<br/>Java + Spring Boot]

    InfraRepo --> Ubuntu[Ubuntu 24.04<br/>Raspberry Pi 5<br/>nexo-raiden-lab-01]
    Ubuntu --> K3s[K3s Kubernetes]

    GitOpsRepo --> ArgoCD[ArgoCD<br/>GitOps Controller]
    ArgoCD --> K3s

    K3s --> MonitoringNS[monitoring namespace]
    MonitoringNS --> Prometheus[Prometheus]
    MonitoringNS --> Grafana[Grafana]
    MonitoringNS --> NodeExporter[Node Exporter]
    MonitoringNS --> ELK[ELK Stack<br/>Elasticsearch + Logstash + Kibana]

    K3s --> SecurityNS[security namespace]
    SecurityNS --> Vault[Vault<br/>Secrets Management]
    SecurityNS --> Trivy[Trivy<br/>Image Scanning]
    SecurityNS --> Gatekeeper[OPA / Gatekeeper<br/>Policy Enforcement]
    SecurityNS --> Cosign[Cosign<br/>Image Signing]

    K3s --> PlatformNS[platform namespace]
    PlatformNS --> Keycloak[Keycloak<br/>Identity and Access]
    PlatformNS --> Ingress[Ingress Controller]
    PlatformNS --> CertManager[cert-manager]

    K3s --> DataNS[data namespace]
    DataNS --> PostgreSQL[PostgreSQL]
    DataNS --> RabbitMQ[RabbitMQ]
    DataNS --> Kafka[Kafka optional]
    DataNS --> MinIO[MinIO optional]

    K3s --> AINS[ai namespace]
    AINS --> Ollama[Ollama]
    AINS --> Qdrant[Qdrant]
    AINS --> RAG[RAG Service]

    K3s --> AppsNS[applications namespace]
    AppsNS --> AccountService[account-service<br/>Java 21 + Spring Boot 3]
    AppsNS --> TransactionService[transaction-service<br/>Java 21 + Spring Boot 3]
    AppsNS --> AuditService[audit-service<br/>Java 21 + Spring Boot 3]
    AppsNS --> OpenAPI[OpenAPI Docs]
    AppsNS --> Flyway[Flyway Migrations]
    AppsNS --> Testcontainers[Testcontainers]

    AccountService --> PostgreSQL
    TransactionService --> PostgreSQL
    TransactionService --> RabbitMQ
    AuditService --> ELK
    AccountService --> Keycloak
    TransactionService --> Keycloak

    Prometheus --> Grafana
    NodeExporter --> Prometheus
    ELK --> Kibana[Kibana Dashboards]
